---
---

<section class="tight" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header" data-reveal>
      <div class="label">About</div>
      <h2 class="display">
        Full-stack engineer<br>from <em>Tanta, Egypt</em><span class="dot">.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="lead">
        Computer Science &amp; Engineering student at <span class="jpn">E-JUST</span>, building production-grade software across
        the stack — from Django monoliths to SwiftUI gaze-controlled interfaces, Laravel e-commerce
        to PyTorch classification models. I bridge engineering and operations, shipping code that
        runs businesses.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-stat" data-reveal>
        <div class="stat-ring solid coral large">11+</div>
        <div><b>Production Systems</b><span>Live in the wild</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-stat" data-reveal>
        <div class="stat-ring solid large">22</div>
        <div><b>ERP Modules</b><span>Across one Django monolith</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-stat" data-reveal>
        <div class="stat-ring solid coral large">5</div>
        <div><b>Spoken Languages</b><span>AR · EN · DE · FR · JP</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-stat" data-reveal>
        <div class="stat-ring solid large">7</div>
        <div><b>Years Engineering</b><span>Since my first build</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .about-stat {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 20px;
    background: var(--bone);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 14px;
  }
  .about-stat b {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .about-stat span {
    font-family: var(--body);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-mute);
  }
  .stat-ring.large {
    width: 44px; height: 44px;
    font-size: 13px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
